data.description: HARD TO FIND. 5 Bedrooms, 4 Bath home with over 4600 sq. ft.  located on a cul-de-sac in the Lake Douglas area has everything your family needs.  As you enter the two-story foyer you are greeted by a beautiful wooden staircase and hardwood floors. There is a formal living room and dining room but the real gathering place for the home is the kitchen. Cozy up to the fireplace in the breakfast room while the cook of the family prepares dinner.  Custom built cabinetry with granite countertop, tons of storage, gas cook top and an island. Adjoining the breakfast room is a large family room with another fireplace and built in cabinets. Or stroll out to the sunroom that features a wall of windows and tons of natural light. The sunroom overlooks the custom grilling area. The primary suite is private and ample on the main level. New walk-in tile shower and new free standing soaking tub, new counter tops, large walk-in closet. There is also an office/ bedroom downstairs that has access to a private full bath. There are 3 large bedrooms upstairs and 2 full bathrooms. Upstairs you could convert one of the bedrooms into a movie theater room. Home features crown molding thru out home, high ceiling, hardwood, brick, and carpet. New updates 2021 roof, HVAC, new kitchen appliances, windows, new front door, hardi board siding, light fixture, ceiling fans, paint inside and out, detached garage storage. This home has one of the largest walk-in attics ever known to man. You will not have to do away with any treasure or keepsakes. You'll enjoy the proximity to shopping, schools, and medical facilities.  Bainbridge is blessed with wonderful recreational water with the Flint River running through it, 25 minutes to the 38,000-acre Lake Seminole (the Bass Capital of the World) and is just 45 minutes from Tallahassee, and 2 hours from the Gulf Coast. You can make this home yours by calling your favorite Realtor or the Listing Agent for more information and to schedule a showing.
